  "riddle": "1. A cinematic gem born from the collaboration of nations — what is the country that nurtured this film's creation?\n\n2. Journey to the vast northern expanse. How high does the ground rise in this land, known for its resilience and complexity?\n\n3. A cultural tapestry unfurls within its borders. Discover how many institutions dedicated to art and history lie in the vicinity of this nation.\n\n4. Gather the values from your previous discoveries: add together the elevation you uncovered in clue 2 and the count of museums you found in clue 3.\n\n5. Many sacred spaces grace this territory. How many houses of worship can be found nearby, echoing faith through the ages?\n\n6. Seek the illustrious figure whose art defined a generation in this international masterpiece. How many years had he graced the world by the time he left it?\n\n7. Within the echo of his legacy lies a binary secret. How many ones adorn the binary representation of the age from clue 6?\n\n8. Cast aside a number found in your past: compute the absolute difference between what you’ve gathered about the heights and the cultural institutions from clues 2 and 3, then reduce it through modulo ten. \n\n  The final answer resolves from the values of clues 2, 3, and 4: compute abs(clue 2 - clue 3) % 10. Your answer will reveal a single digit, from 0 to 9.",
